早在2010年3月，即有討論到拍攝《[[超世紀封神榜|超世紀封神榜]]》續集的計劃。在首部電影中飾演[[阿瑞斯|阿瑞斯]]的{{link-en|塔梅爾·哈桑|Tamer Hassan}}於全球首映式上表示「他們希望這部電影能有好表現，使他們能繼續拍攝續集《Return of the Gods》。」<ref>{{cite web| last=Sharp| first=Craig| date=2010-03-29| title=FilmShaft Exclusive! The Stars Align For Clash Of The Titans World Premiere With The SEQUEL Waiting In The Wings| url=http://www.filmshaft.com/exclusive-the-stars-align-for-clash-of-the-titans-world-premiere-with-the-sequel-waiting-in-the-wings/| work=FilmShaft| accessdate=2011-03-23| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110207091746/http://www.filmshaft.com/exclusive-the-stars-align-for-clash-of-the-titans-world-premiere-with-the-sequel-waiting-in-the-wings/| archivedate=2011-02-07}}</ref>。4月，據報導，導演[[路易斯·賴托瑞|路易斯·賴托瑞]]不會再次任職導演，但會擔任續集的執行製片人。該報導還指出，主演[[山姆·沃辛頓|山姆·沃辛頓]]將會回歸，而[[葛瑞格·貝蘭提|葛瑞格·貝蘭提]]則為故事執筆<ref>{{cite web| last=Flemming| first=Mike| date=2010-04-27| title=Sequels For 'Clash Of The Titans' And 'Journey To The Center Of The Earth'| url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/04/creative-lineup-shuffles-loom-for-clash-of-the-titans-and-journey-to-the-center-of-the-earth-sequels/| work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]| accessdate=2011-03-23| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110127140903/http://www.deadline.com/2010/04/creative-lineup-shuffles-loom-for-clash-of-the-titans-and-journey-to-the-center-of-the-earth-sequels/| archivedate=2011-01-27}}</ref>。

6月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]聘請{{link-en|大衛·萊斯利·強森|David Leslie Johnson}}和{{link-en|丹·謬澤|Dan Mazeau}}擔任編劇，巴茲爾·伊萬雅克以製片人身分回歸<ref name="sequel1"/>。電影不會採取後期轉製為3D的方式，而是在拍攝過程中直接以3D格式攝影<ref name="sequel1">{{cite web| last=McNary| first=Dave| date=2010-06-11| title='Clash of the Titans' sequel in the works| url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118020534?refCatId=13| work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]| accessdate=2011-03-23| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107225411/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118020534?refCatId=13| archivedate=2012-11-07}}</ref>。8月，《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》報導，[[乔纳森·理贝斯曼|強納森·李伯斯曼]]簽約擔任續集導演<ref>{{cite web| date=2010-08-31| title=Liebesman Confirmed for Clash of the Titans 2| url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=69406| work=ComingSoon.net| publisher={{link-en|CraveOnline|CraveOnline}}| accessdate=2011-03-23| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100901211351/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=69406| archivedate=2010-09-01}}</ref>。

9月，導演強納森·李伯斯曼證實山姆·沃辛頓、[[潔瑪·艾特頓|潔瑪·艾特頓]]、[[雷夫·范恩斯|雷夫·范恩斯]]及[[連恩·尼遜|連恩·尼遜]]都將再次出演續集<ref>{{cite web| date=2010-09-11| title="Clash of the Titans 2" to Bring Back Ralph Fiennes and Liam Neeson| url=http://www.worstpreviews.com/headline.php?id=18953| work=WorstPreviews| accessdate=2012-04-24| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100913214324/http://www.worstpreviews.com/headline.php?id=18953| archivedate=2010-09-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| last=Douglas| first=Edward| date=2010-09-10| title=Clash of the Titans 2 and Expendables 2 Updates| url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=69713| work=ComingSoon.net| publisher={{link-en|CraveOnline|CraveOnline}}| accessdate=2011-03-23| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110904041528/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=69713| archivedate=2011-09-04}}</ref>。然而，基於不明原因，艾特頓退出了續集<ref>{{cite web| date=2011-03-30| title=Gemma Arterton Out Of Clash Of The Titans Sequel| url=http://www.contactmusic.com/gemma-arterton/news/gemma-arterton-out-of-clash-of-the-titans-sequel_1210178| work={{link-en|Contactmusic.com|Contactmusic.com}}| accessdate=2011-03-30| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409110819/http://www.contactmusic.com/gemma-arterton/news/gemma-arterton-out-of-clash-of-the-titans-sequel_1210178| archivedate=2017-04-09}}</ref>，她所飾演的角色[[伊俄|伊俄]]被設定為在續集中過世。12月，連恩·尼遜透露片名將定為《Wrath of the Titans》，預計隔年3月開始拍攝<ref>{{cite web| last=Showbiz| first=Bang| date=2010-12-07| title=Neeson looks forward to Titans 2| url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/news/neeson-looks-forward-to-titans-2-15023873.html| work={{link-en|貝爾法斯特電訊報|Belfast Telegraph|The Belfast Telegraph}}| publisher={{link-en|獨立新聞媒體|Independent News & Media|Independent News & Media}}| accessdate=2011-03-24| archive-date=2010-12-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211093828/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/news/neeson-looks-forward-to-titans-2-15023873.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年1月，據報導，[[艾格·拉米瑞茲|艾格·拉米瑞茲]]和[[托比·凱貝爾|托比·凱貝爾]]分別在為出演[[阿瑞斯|阿瑞斯]]和{{link-en|阿戈諾爾|Agenor}}一事進行談判<ref name="sequelcasting1">{{cite web| last=Sneider| first=Jeff| date=2011-01-07| title=Exclusive: Ramirez, Kebbell to Join 'Titans' Sequel; Atwell Testing| url=http://www.thewrap.com/exclusive-ramirez-kebbell-join-titans-sequel-atwell-testing-23713/| work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]| accessdate=2011-01-07| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305121625/http://www.thewrap.com/exclusive-ramirez-kebbell-join-titans-sequel-atwell-testing-23713/| archivedate=2017-03-05}}</ref>。還有報導指出，[[比爾·奈伊|比爾·奈伊]]正討論是否將飾演[[赫淮斯托斯|赫淮斯托斯]]一角<ref name="sequelcasting1"/>。此外，[[海莉·艾特沃|海莉·艾特沃]]也在[[安德洛墨達|安德洛墨達]]一角的{{link-en|試鏡|Screen test}}候選人名單內<ref name="sequelcasting1"/>，而於前作飾演該角的[[艾莉克莎·黛沃洛斯|艾莉克莎·黛沃洛斯]]因與其他電影的時間安排衝突而退出<ref name="Alexa Davalos"/>。其它安德洛墨達的考慮人選包含{{link-en|喬治娜·海格|Georgina Haig}}、[[詹妮特·蒙哥馬利|詹妮特·蒙哥馬利]]、{{link-en|多米妮克·麥克艾麗戈特|Dominique McElligott}}及[[克蕾曼絲·波西|克蕾曼絲·波西]]等人<ref name="sequelcasting1"/>。

