《怒戰天神》的[[藍光光碟|藍光]]、3D藍光、[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]及數位下載版本於2012年6月26日發布<ref>{{cite web |date=2012-05-15 |last=Shaffer |first=R.L. |title=Wrath of the Titans to Conquer BD, DVD |url=http://bluray.ign.com/articles/122/1224676p1.html |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120518004002/http://bluray.ign.com/articles/122/1224676p1.html |archivedate=2012-05-18 |accessdate=2012-05-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 取消續集 ==

2011年11月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]聘請《怒戰天神》的編劇{{link-en|丹·謬澤|Dan Mazeau}}及{{link-en|大衛·萊斯利·強森|David Leslie Johnson}}為第三部電影《Revenge of the Titans》進行發展及編寫前期綱要的工作，當時《怒戰天神》還在後期製作的階段<ref>{{cite web |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=2011-11-02 |title=Warner Bros. Readying 'Clash of the Titans 3' (Exclusive) |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/clash-of-the-titans-3-warner-bros-256828 |work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2011-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DX9cHSxD?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/clash-of-the-titans-3-warner-bros-256828 |archivedate=2013-01-09 }}</ref>。2013年春天，[[山姆·沃辛頓|山姆·沃辛頓]]表示他不認為會製作第三部電影<ref>{{cite web|title="Sam Worthington Talks AVATAR Sequels, Working with Schwarzenegger on TEN, How He Doesn’t Think There Will be a Third CLASH OF THE TITANS, and More"|url=http://collider.com/avatar-2-3-sequels-sam-worthington/|work=Collider.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130504023523/http://collider.com/avatar-2-3-sequels-sam-worthington/|archivedate=2013-05-04|accessdate=2013-05-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>。由於兩部電影的評價不佳，以及缺乏對劇本的想法，該電影而後被取消<ref name="Clash of the Titans 3"/>。

